{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "8c97823e-0711-4425-94c2-ab2a39a8ee7f", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/8c97823e-0711-4425-94c2-ab2a39a8ee7f@1.pkg/1772602358236/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602359364", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/8c97823e-0711-4425-94c2-ab2a39a8ee7f@1.pkg/1772602358236/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602359364"}, "identifier": "8c97823e-0711-4425-94c2-ab2a39a8ee7f", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>A.有误，“朔气传金柝，寒光照铁衣”这两句描写出木兰在边塞军营的艰苦生活，选项“描写了路途的遥远和军队行进的神速”表述错误；</p>\n\n<p>B.正确；</p>\n\n<p>C.有误，《木兰诗》是一首叙事诗，叙述了一个传奇的故事，选项“抒情诗”表述错误；</p>\n\n<p>D.有误，这两句运用对偶和互文的修辞手法，概述了将士们征战多年，历经许多战斗，很多将士战死沙场，木兰等许多将士胜利归来，选项“许多将军战死沙场，许多壮士胜利归来”表述错误；</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p>下列关于《木兰诗》的表述正确的一项是（　　）</p>\n", "title": "下列关于《木兰诗》的表述正确的一项是（　　）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["B"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/8c97823e-0711-4425-94c2-ab2a39a8ee7f@1.pkg/item.json?v=1750865011462", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "choice_type": "character", "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>“朔气传金柝，寒光照铁衣。”这两句对偶工整，描写了路途的遥远和军队行进的神速。</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>“爷娘闻女来，出郭相扶将；阿姊闻妹来，当户理红妆；小弟闻姊来，磨刀霍霍向猪羊”，这几句运用排比的修辞手法，描写了木兰归家时家人忙碌的情景，烘托了欢乐的气氛。</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>《木兰诗》是一首抒情诗，全诗以木兰是女郎来构思木兰的传奇故事，富有浪漫色彩。</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<p>“将军百战死，壮士十年归。”这两句是说征战多年，许多将军战死沙场，许多壮士胜利归来，体现出战争的旷日持久与战斗的激烈悲壮。</p>\n"}], "prompt": "<p>下列关于《木兰诗》的表述正确的一项是（　　）</p>\n", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "tags": ["$M002000000", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a749654-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "ff8080814371757b014390fcdce504bd", "5136342960", "$RE0000", "$M003002000", "5036342749", "$RE0200", "$RE0201", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "44bebf7c-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a749654-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "ff8080814371757b014390fcdce504bd", "5136342960", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "44bebf7c-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4"], "status": "ONLINE", "is_publish": false, "id": "8c97823e-0711-4425-94c2-ab2a39a8ee7f", "global_title": {"zh-CN": "下列关于《木兰诗》的表述正确的一项是（　　）"}, "global_description": {"zh-CN": "<p>下列关于《木兰诗》的表述正确的一项是（　　）</p>\n"}, "global_keywords": {}, "global_label": {}, "custom_properties": {"sys_packing_status": "ready", "preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/8c97823e-0711-4425-94c2-ab2